        "liquid": "<div class=\"ugc-section\">\n  <div class=\"ugc-header\">\n    <h2>Ils respirent enfin un air sain</h2>\n    <div class=\"ugc-trust-line\">\n      <span class=\"ugc-trust-stars\" aria-hidden=\"true\">★★★★★</span>\n      <span>4,8/5 · Avis clients vérifiés</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"ugc-slider\">\n\n    <!-- AVIS 1 — Marie -->\n    <div class=\"ugc-card\">\n      <div class=\"ugc-card-header\">\n        <div class=\"ugc-avatar mc-teal\">M</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-user-info\">\n          <span class=\"ugc-name\">Marie D.</span>\n          <span class=\"ugc-loc\">📍 Toulouse</span>\n          <span class=\"ugc-verified\"><svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#27ae60\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z\"></path></svg> Achat vérifié</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ugc-photo-container\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0990/1765/4619/files/aivs_3.png?v=1769998606\" class=\"ugc-photo\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Avant après moisissure chambre enfants\">\n        <div class=\"photo-badge\">📷 Photo envoyée</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ugc-content\">\n        <div class=\"ugc-stars\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5\">★★★★★</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-tag\">👶 Chambre enfants</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-text\">\"Moisissure noire dans la chambre de mes enfants depuis 2 ans. Tous les sprays revenaient après 3 semaines. Avec Moisissure-CLEAN, après 5 semaines le mur est sec. <strong>Mes enfants toussent beaucoup moins la nuit.</strong>\"</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-date\">Il y a 5 jours</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- AVIS 2 — Jean-Claude -->\n    <div class=\"ugc-card\">\n      <div class=\"ugc-card-header\">\n        <div class=\"ugc-avatar mc-navy\">J</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-user-info\">\n          <span class=\"ugc-name\">Jean-Claude R.</span>\n          <span class=\"ugc-loc\">📍 Lyon</span>\n          <span class=\"ugc-verified\"><svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#27ae60\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z\"></path></svg> Achat vérifié</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ugc-photo-container\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0990/1765/4619/files/avis_2.png?v=1769998060\" class=\"ugc-photo\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Avant après salle de bain\">\n        <div class=\"photo-badge\">📷 Photo envoyée</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ugc-content\">\n        <div class=\"ugc-stars\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5\">★★★★★</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-tag\">🚿 Salle de bain</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-text\">\"À 67 ans, je n'avais plus la force de frotter les murs chaque semaine. Installation en 2 minutes, branché et laissé faire. <strong>6 semaines plus tard, le mur est sec et propre.</strong> Ça ne consomme presque rien.\"</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-date\">Il y a 8 jours</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- AVIS 3 — Lucas & Emma -->\n    <div class=\"ugc-card\">\n      <div class=\"ugc-card-header\">\n        <div class=\"ugc-avatar mc-green\">L</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-user-info\">\n          <span class=\"ugc-name\">Lucas & Emma</span>\n          <span class=\"ugc-loc\">📍 Nantes</span>\n          <span class=\"ugc-verified\"><svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#27ae60\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z\"></path></svg> Achat vérifié</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ugc-photo-container\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0990/1765/4619/files/avis_4.png?v=1769998897\" class=\"ugc-photo\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Avant après moisissure derrière meuble\">\n        <div class=\"photo-badge\">📷 Photo envoyée</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ugc-content\">\n        <div class=\"ugc-stars\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5\">★★★★★</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-tag\">🏠 Location</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-text\">\"On est locataires, le proprio refusait les travaux. On a installé Moisissure-CLEAN avec les pieds, sans percer. <strong>Le mur est sec, plus d'odeur.</strong> On peut enfin recevoir des amis sans avoir honte.\"</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-date\">Il y a 12 jours</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- AVIS 4 — Thomas -->\n    <div class=\"ugc-card\">\n      <div class=\"ugc-card-header\">\n        <div class=\"ugc-avatar mc-orange\">T</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-user-info\">\n          <span class=\"ugc-name\">Thomas B.</span>\n          <span class=\"ugc-loc\">📍 Bordeaux</span>\n          <span class=\"ugc-verified\"><svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#27ae60\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z\"></path></svg> Achat vérifié</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ugc-content\">\n        <div class=\"ugc-stars\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5\">★★★★★</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-tag\">🏢 Propriétaire bailleur</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-text\">\"3 appartements en location, une fortune en peinture et produits chaque année. J'ai équipé mes 3 biens. <strong>8 mois, zéro problème, zéro plainte des locataires.</strong> Économies énormes sur les réparations.\"</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-date\">Il y a 6 jours</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- AVIS 5 — Sophie -->\n    <div class=\"ugc-card\">\n      <div class=\"ugc-card-header\">\n        <div class=\"ugc-avatar mc-purple\">S</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-user-info\">\n          <span class=\"ugc-name\">Sophie M.</span>\n          <span class=\"ugc-loc\">📍 Lille</span>\n          <span class=\"ugc-verified\"><svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#27ae60\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z\"></path></svg> Achat vérifié</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ugc-photo-container\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0990/1765/4619/files/avis_5.png?v=1769999132\" class=\"ugc-photo\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Avant après chambre\">\n        <div class=\"photo-badge\">📷 Photo envoyée</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ugc-content\">\n        <div class=\"ugc-stars\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5\">★★★★★</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-tag\">🫁 Allergies respiratoires</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-text\">\"Allergique, crises d'asthme à cause de la moisissure dans ma chambre. Mon médecin m'a conseillé l'infrarouge. <strong>Après 6 semaines, la moisissure a disparu.</strong> Je ne prends presque plus mes médicaments.\"</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-date\">Il y a 3 jours</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- AVIS 6 — Patrick -->\n    <div class=\"ugc-card\">\n      <div class=\"ugc-card-header\">\n        <div class=\"ugc-avatar mc-navy\">P</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-user-info\">\n          <span class=\"ugc-name\">Patrick V.</span>\n          <span class=\"ugc-loc\">📍 Strasbourg</span>\n          <span class=\"ugc-verified\"><svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#27ae60\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z\"></path></svg> Achat vérifié</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ugc-photo-container\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0990/1765/4619/files/download.jpg?v=1769999562\" class=\"ugc-photo\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Avant après cave\">\n        <div class=\"photo-badge\">📷 Photo envoyée</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ugc-content\">\n        <div class=\"ugc-stars\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5\">★★★★★</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-tag\">🏚️ Cave</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-text\">\"Cave inutilisable, toujours humide, moisissure partout. Impossible de stocker quoi que ce soit. <strong>2 panneaux, 2 mois : murs secs.</strong> Je peux enfin ranger mes affaires sans qu'elles moisissent.\"</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-date\">Il y a 11 jours</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- AVIS 7 — Nathalie -->\n    <div class=\"ugc-card\">\n      <div class=\"ugc-card-header\">\n        <div class=\"ugc-avatar mc-teal\">N</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-user-info\">\n          <span class=\"ugc-name\">Nathalie F.</span>\n          <span class=\"ugc-loc\">📍 Marseille</span>\n          <span class=\"ugc-verified\"><svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#27ae60\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z\"></path></svg> Achat vérifié</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ugc-content\">\n        <div class=\"ugc-stars\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5\">★★★★★</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-tag\">💰 970€ économisés</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-text\">\"J'ai calculé : 970€ en sprays et peinture anti-moisissure en 3 ans. Tout revenait au même endroit. <strong>59,90€ le panneau, branché une fois, et le mur est sec depuis 4 mois.</strong> J'aurais dû commencer par là.\"</div>\n        <div class=\"ugc-date\">Il y a 4 jours</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n  .ugc-section {\n    padding: 30px 0;\n    background-color: #F9FAFB;\n    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n  .ugc-header {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 18px;\n    padding: 0 16px;\n  }\n  .ugc-header h2 {\n    font-size: 20px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #1A1A1A;\n    margin: 0 0 6px;\n  }\n  .ugc-trust-line {\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: #555;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 6px;\n  }\n  .ugc-trust-stars {\n    color: #27ae60;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    line-height: 1;\n  }\n\n  /* Slider */\n  .ugc-slider {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 12px;\n    overflow-x: auto;\n    padding: 8px 16px 24px;\n    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    scrollbar-width: none;\n  }\n  .ugc-slider::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }\n\n  /* Carte */\n  .ugc-card {\n    flex: 0 0 260px;\n    scroll-snap-align: center;\n    background: #FFF;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\n    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n  }\n\n  /* Header */\n  .ugc-card-header {\n    padding: 10px 12px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6;\n  }\n\n  /* Avatar lettre */\n  .ugc-avatar {\n    width: 34px;\n    height: 34px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    margin-right: 10px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    color: #FFF;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n  .mc-teal   { background: #00A4C1; }\n  .mc-navy   { background: #1E3A5F; }\n  .mc-green  { background: #16A34A; }\n  .mc-orange { background: #EA580C; }\n  .mc-purple { background: #7C3AED; }\n\n  .ugc-user-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }\n  .ugc-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #1A1A1A; }\n  .ugc-loc { font-size: 10px; color: #888; margin: 1px 0; }\n  .ugc-verified { font-size: 10px; color: #27ae60; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 3px; }\n\n  /* Photo */\n  .ugc-photo-container {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 180px;\n    background: #F3F4F6;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .ugc-photo {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    object-fit: cover;\n  }\n  .photo-badge {\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 6px;\n    right: 6px;\n    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55);\n    color: #FFF;\n    font-size: 9px;\n    padding: 3px 6px;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    backdrop-filter: blur(2px);\n  }\n\n  /* Contenu */\n  .ugc-content {\n    padding: 10px 12px;\n    flex-grow: 1;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n  }\n  .ugc-stars {\n    color: #27ae60;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    margin-bottom: 4px;\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n  }\n  .ugc-tag {\n    display: inline-block;\n    font-size: 10px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #00A4C1;\n    background: #E0F7FA;\n    padding: 2px 8px;\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    margin-bottom: 6px;\n    width: fit-content;\n  }\n  .ugc-text {\n    font-size: 12px;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n    color: #444;\n    margin-bottom: 6px;\n  }\n  .ugc-text strong {\n    color: #1A1A1A;\n    font-weight: 700;\n  }\n  .ugc-date {\n    font-size: 10px;\n    color: #999;\n    margin-top: auto;\n  }\n\n  @media(min-width: 750px) {\n    .ugc-header h2 { font-size: 26px; }\n    .ugc-card { flex: 0 0 300px; }\n    .ugc-photo-container { height: 220px; }\n    .ugc-text { font-size: 13px; }\n  }\n</style>",
